<div>
  <h2>The Challenge:</h2>
  <div class="side-by-side">
    <p>
      1. Fortnite OG was an emotional return for longtime players. The challenge
      was creating a visual identity and event branding that evoked nostalgia
      while still feeling fresh, exciting, and competition-ready.
    </p>
    <p>
      2. The event needed a cohesive motion package that extended across
      trailers, social content, live broadcasts, and in-game elements—all while
      seamlessly integrating with Fortnite’s evolving brand.
    </p>
    <p>
      3. With Fortnite’s biggest names streaming the event, the branding needed
      to ensure strong visibility, high retention, and a shareable, hype-driven
      experience.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

