<div>
  <h2>The Solution:</h2>

  <div class="side-by-side">
    <div>
      <p class="big">Let Them Eat Cake</p>
      <p>
        To capture the spirit of The Reunion, I directed a high-energy animated
        announcement trailer with a nostalgic, celebratory atmosphere that hyped
        up both players and fans. The concept? A massive Fortnite-themed cake
        representing the OG map, in all its glory, with charming cake-toppers
        marking the old landmarks players loved.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="big">A Motion System That Tastes as Good as It Looks</p>
      <p>
        I worked closely with Epic Games to ensure every map detail would truly
        reflect the OG update’s return, coordinating with them to learn which
        iconic landmarks would return to Fortnite's ever-changing world. With
        the cake as the centerpiece, I led the development of a dynamic,
        high-energy motion system making every broadcast screen feel like an
        extension of Fortnite, seamlessly bringing the event together over
        dessert.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
